<define-tag description>security update</define-tag>
<define-tag moreinfo>
<p>It was discovered that the TLS server in Erlang is vulnerable to an
adaptive chosen ciphertext attack against RSA keys.</p>

<p>For the oldstable distribution (jessie), this problem has been fixed
in version 1:17.3-dfsg-4+deb8u2.</p>

<p>For the stable distribution (stretch), this problem has been fixed in
version 1:19.2.1+dfsg-2+deb9u1.</p>

<p>We recommend that you upgrade your erlang packages.</p>

<p>For the detailed security status of erlang please refer to
its security tracker page at:
<a href="https://security-tracker.debian.org/tracker/erlang">\
https://security-tracker.debian.org/tracker/erlang</a></p>
</define-tag>

